<h2>🚀 Version 0.2.4</h2>

<h3>✨ What's New</h3>

<table>
<tr>
<td width="50px">☁️</td>
<td>
<strong>AWS S3 Support</strong><br>
Added <code>aws-sdk-s3</code> gem to enable S3 storage for file uploads. This allows the application to store uploaded files in AWS S3 instead of the local filesystem, providing scalable and reliable cloud storage.
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>🤖</td>
<td>
<strong>Default Agent Update</strong><br>
Changed the default agent from "llamabot" to "leo". The agent system is now more streamlined with "leo" as the primary agent for interactions.
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>🧹</td>
<td>
<strong>Code Cleanup</strong><br>
Simplified agent configuration structure by removing the unnecessary <code>RailsBasic</code> module wrapper and moving <code>AgentStateBuilder</code> to a top-level class. This makes the codebase cleaner and easier to maintain.
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>🐳</td>
<td>
<strong>Docker Improvements</strong><br>
Enhanced multi-platform build support (ARM64/x86_64) by making the Docker build configuration more flexible. Removed hardcoded platform arguments to support both Apple Silicon and Intel architectures.
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>📝</td>
<td>
<strong>Documentation</strong><br>
Added dev notes tracking system in <code>docs/</code> folder to maintain better records of changes across releases.
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<h3>🔧 Technical Details</h3>

<ul>
